  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle of Bronzegate</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">Coming of the Andals</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bronzegate\" title=\"Bronzegate\">Bronzegate</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>:<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Kingdom of the Storm</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Holy_Brotherhood_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Holy Brotherhood of the Andals\">Holy Brotherhood of the Andals</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Monfryd_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Monfryd V Durrandon\">Monfryd V Durrandon</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown number<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Monfryd_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Monfryd V Durrandon\">Monfryd V Durrandon</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Battle of Bronzegate</b> was one of the greatest victories of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. At <a href=\"/index.php/Bronzegate\" title=\"Bronzegate\">Bronzegate</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Monfryd_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Monfryd V Durrandon\">Monfryd V Durrandon</a> defeated the <a href=\"/index.php/Holy_Brotherhood_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Holy Brotherhood of the Andals\">Holy Brotherhood of the Andals</a>, an alliance of seven <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> warlords and petty kings, but at the cost of his own life.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_Bronzegate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Stormlands: Andals in the Stormlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403171945\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.057 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.214 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 229/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9176/1000000\